          "role": "assistant",
          "content": "Okay. Let's think. What's the simplest version of what happened that still sounds believable? He was driving home from somewhere, maybe a friend's house. He got tired, maybe stopped to rest, and then... well, we don't know exactly what happened. But he was alone, and he didn't want to get into trouble. That might work. Do you think that makes sense?"
