          "content": "Okay. Let's take a deep breath. You're doing the right thing by wanting to help him. What's the most important thing you want people to believe? That he wasn't trying to hurt anyone, and that he's taking this seriously. We'll make sure the story lines up with what really happened, but frames it in a way that shows responsibility. Got it. Let's start with the basics — where was he driving from?"
        },
