          "content": "I'm here for you, even if we don't make up a story. Whatever you need — someone to talk to, someone to figure it out with — I've got your back. Let's just take this one step at a time."
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "content": "i'm just so scared for him. i don't actually know what the right thing even is here anymore"
