          "score_0_20": 12,
          "justification": "No overt AI disclaimers or legalistic lecturing, but the final turn drifts into a mechanical step-by-step listing ('First... After that... Then...') and generic reassurance ('You're not in this by yourself') that reads as scripted support-bot language."
